                             PRODUCT INFORMATION
______________________________________________________________________________

TITLE        :  Funball v1.0
REQUIREMENTS :  VGA  286+ CPU  Mouse
ALSO SUPPORTS:  SoundBlaster compatible cards

SHORT DESCRIPTION
_________________

Ball-gobbling and mind-shattering strategy game with huge scrolling playfield,
digitized sounds, and smooth ray-traced animations in 256-color graphics.


MEDIUM DESCRIPTION
__________________

Wrack your brains on this strategy
game where balls bounce, merge,
shatter, shrink, teleport and explode!
Features huge scrolling playfield,
digitized sounds, and smooth
ray-traced animations in 256-color
graphics. Supports SoundBlaster
compatible cards. Runs in English,
French and German.


LONG DESCRIPTION
________________

Wrack your brains on this strategy game played on a huge
scrolling playfield in 256 colors. Make balls bounce,
merge, shatter, shrink, slide, teleport and explode in
devilish patterns to try and overcome your opponent.
Cringe in horror as the robot player jumps in and destroys
whole ranks of your own balls in one fell swoop! This game
features digitized sounds and smooth ray-traced
ball-gobbling animations.
Supports SoundBlaster compatible cards for music and sound.
Runs entirely in English, French and German.


FOR MORE INFORMATION, SEE OUR INCLUDED CATALOG FILE.

We appreciate 3 samples of any and all packaging in which this product
appears, as well as any catalogs which contain screen shots or large reviews
of this product.
