                             ATTENTION SYSOPS!
______________________________________________________________________________

Become an official BBS distribution site for Impulse Games!  Attract new
callers and give your regular callers a place to find all the latest Impulse
releases.

In our upcoming releases, we are going to be pushing the creative edge to
bring the world original games using new software technology and ideas.  The
future of video games is virtual reality - true 3D interaction, and we're
going to be on the leading edge.  We want you to be there with us.

Our ansi screens will add a professional look to your BBS, our games will
bring you more callers, and you will help us by spreading our games to the
world!

To become an official Impulse Games distribution site:

1. Have all of our latest titles readily available on your BBS.
   For a list of our titles, see the file "ORDERFRM.TXT" in any of our
   games.  All our latest releases are available to you as FREE downloads
   from the Software Creations BBS.

2. Check Software Creations for our latest releases, and update your BBS!

3. Several Impulse ansi screens are available which may be used freely
   throughout your BBS.  These screens are in our latest Sysop Pack
   (SYSPACK1.ZIP) which is avaiable on Software Creations.  We recommend
   using one or many of these ansi files containing our logo (or design
   your own), to let your users know to come to your BBS for the latest
   Impulse releases.
   These screens have been designed with a professional style, and are easy
   to read at a glance.  You may freely modify our ansi screens as long as
   they maintain the original intended use.

Once you have an Impulse Games file section set up on your BBS, you may
wish to register with us as an official site.  As an official site,
we will post your BBS name and number in our bulletin, letting people
know where they can get our games in your calling area!  To register,
call Software Creations and type "OPEN 4" to fill out the script with
information about your BBS.

Carrying our games will give you an edge over your competition, and bring
you more paying users.  Take a few minutes to become a release site for some
of the highest quality new games in shareware- you won't be disappointed.
Thank you, and if you have any questions, don't hesitate to contact us.

Adam Pedersen, President
Impulse Games
